text.section:
The Council shall:
make grants in accordance with § 5-504 of this subtitle;
establish or assist in the establishment of programs designed to reduce the incidence of firearms violence related crime and encourage participation in existing programs with these objectives;
identify specific goals, objectives, and methodologies to be used in support of programs eligible for funding under this subtitle;
identify priorities for firearms violence related crime prevention strategies in the State; and
develop criteria to evaluate the outcomes of programs that receive money under this subtitle.
